Package: atv
Type: Package
Title: Tools for handling acoustic televiewer data
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Jonathan Kennel, Beth Parker
Maintainer: Jonathan Kennel <jkennel@uoguelph.ca>
Description: These are a few tools for working with acoustic televiewer (ATV) data in r. Methods are designed to be function efficiently and to be an open source utility for handling ATV data.
